commit_message:
refactor some fip methods for df

1. The update/delete_floatingip code looks a bit complex in
df_local_controller, we could do some optimize work;

2. Change some methods to inner methods for dnat app;

3. Adjust corresponding UT code.

Change-Id: Ic90307b9dfddf2add79149f8edd0ca55d97618ad

